          "INC-SPECT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Simulation system was checked by data of neutron",
                "spectra produced by",
                "- monoenergetic proton beams as measured by Ratynski+",
                "and Lederer+ ;",
                "-broadened beam proton as measured by Feinberg+",
                " (see REL-REFs).",
                " The simulated neutron spectra compared to the MBNS at",
                " kT = 30 keV are on Fig.2 of J,NDS,120,205,2014.",
                " 96% of the neutrons passed through the Au frontal",
                " surface; 95% through the Tb frontal surface,",
                " 93% through the Tb back surface. Fluence ratio Au/Tb",
                " was estimated to be equal to 1.02."
              ]
            }
          ],
